# Internal working notes — keep these out of the public repository.
# Drafts, prompts, handoffs, status reports and planning docs belong in local
# scratch space, not in a release. Anything genuinely useful to a contributor
# goes in docs/ as a proper document instead.
/HANDOFF.md
/FINAL_REPORT.md
/REPORT.md
/NOTES.md
/TODO.md
/SCRATCH.md
/*_prompt*.md
/*_PROMPT*.md
/docs/STATUS.md
/docs/IMPLEMENTATION_CHECKLIST.md
/docs/superpowers/
/docs/internal/
/docs/drafts/
/.notes/
/.scratch/
/scratch/

# Credentials and keys — never commit these
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
*.jks
id_rsa
id_ed25519
credentials.json
